Package: wmwAUC
Title: Wilcoxon-Mann-Whitney Test of No Group Discrimination (Continuous Variables)
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-11-28
Authors@R:
    person("Marian", "Grendar", , "marian.grendar@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6712-3457"))
Description: Provides inference for the Wilcoxon-Mann-Whitney test under the null hypothesis
        H0: AUC = 0.5 for continuous random variables. Traditional implementations test
        H0: F = G, which is inappropriately broad and leads to poorly calibrated inference.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/grendar/wmwAUC
BugReports: https://github.com/grendar/wmwAUC/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
